{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">测定强酸与强碱反应的反应热。</span></p>"},{"title":"用品","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">仪器：保温烧杯、量筒、木盖、环形玻璃搅拌棒、温度计。</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">药品：氢氧化钠溶液、稀盐酸。</span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">1.用一个量筒量取</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">50ml 0.5mol/L</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">盐酸，倒入小烧杯中，并用温度计测量盐酸温度，记入表中。</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">2.用另一个量筒量取</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">50ml 0.55mol/L</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">氢氧化钠溶液，并用温度计测量溶液温度，记入表中。</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">3.温度计和环形玻璃搅拌棒放入烧杯中，然后倒入氢氧化钠溶液，迅速盖上盖板，搅拌溶液，并记录混合溶液的最高温度</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><em>t</em><sub>2</sub></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">，记入表中。</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">4.重复</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">2~4</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">次，计算盐酸和氢氧化钠溶液的初始温度的平均值</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><em>t</em><sub>1</sub></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">，根据下式计算中和热。</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">&Delta;<em>H</em>=-16.72(<em>t</em><sub>2</sub>-<em>t</em><sub>1</sub>)kJ/mol</span></span></p>"},{"title":"数据","data":"<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:600px\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">实验次数</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"3\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">起始温度<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><em>t</em><sub>1</sub>/℃</span></span></td>\n\t\t\t<td rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">终止温度</span></p>\n\n\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><em>t</em><sub>2</sub>/℃</span></span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">温度差</span></p>\n\n\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">(<em>t</em><sub>2</sub>-<em>t</em><sub>1</sub>)/℃</span></span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">HCl</span></span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">NaOH</span></span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">平均值</span></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">1</span></span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">2</span></span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">3</span></span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}